      'It was narrated that Adi bin Hatim said:\n&ldquo;I said: O Messenger of Allah, we hunt game but we cannot find anything but the sharp edge of a stone or stick (with which to slaughter it). He said: Cause the blood to flow with whatever you want, and mention the Name of Allah over it.&rdquo;',
