      'Abu Hurairah narrated that Abu Bakr bin Abu Quhafah narrated that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said to him and to Umar:\n&ldquo;Let us go out to Waqifi.&rdquo; He said: &ldquo;So we went out in the moonlight until we came to the garden and he (the owner of the garden) said: Welcome. Then he took up the knife and went among the sheep (to choose one for slaughter), and the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said: Avoid those that are lactating.&rdquo;',
