      'It was narrated that Abu Hurairah said:\n&ldquo;We went out with the Prophet (ﷺ) for Hajj or Umrah, and we encountered a swarm of locusts or a type of locust. We started hitting them with out whips and sandals. The Prophet (ﷺ) said: Eat them for they are the game of the sea.&rdquo;',
