      'Umm Sad said:\n&ldquo;The Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) entered upon Aishah, when I was with her, and said: Is there any food? She said: We have bread, dates and vinegar. The Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said: What a blessed condiment vinegar is. O Allah, bless vinegar, for it was the condiment of the Prophets before me, and no house will ever be poor in which there is vinegar.&rdquo;',
