    hadithEnglish:
      'It was narrated from Uqbah bin Amir Al-Juhani that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;Do not force your sick ones to eat or drink. Allah will feed them and give them to drink.&rdquo;',
