      '\nIt was narrated from Abu Malih AL-HUdhail that some women from the people of Hims asked permission to enter upon Aisha. She said:\nPerhaps you are among those (women) who enter bathhouses? I heard the Messenger of Allah(ﷺ) say: Any woman who takes off her clothes anywhere but in her husbands house, has torn the screen between her and Allah.',
