      'It was narrated from Abdullah bin Umar concerning the dream of the Prophet (ﷺ) that he (the Prophet (ﷺ)) said:\n&ldquo;I saw a black woman with disheveled hair, who left Al-Madinah and went to stay in Al- Mahyaah, which is Juhfah. I interpreted it as referring to an epidemic in Al-Madinah which moved to Juhfah.&rdquo;',
