    hadithEnglish:
      'Abbad bin Kathir Ash-Shami narrated from a woman among them, called Fasilah, that she heard her father say:\n&ldquo;I asked the Prophet (ﷺ): O Messenger of Allah, is it tribalism if a man loves his people? He said: No, rather tribalism is when a man helps his people to do wrong.&rdquo;',
