    hadithEnglish:
      'It was narrated from Awf bin Malik that the Messenger of Allah(ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;The Jews split into seventy-one sects, one of which will be in Paradise and seventy in Hell. The Christians split into seventy-two sects, seventy-one of which will be in Hell and one in Paradise. I swear by the One Whose Hand is the soul of Muhammad, my nation will split into seventy-three sects, one of which will be in Paradise and seventy-two in Hell.&rdquo; It was said: &ldquo;O Messenger of Allah, who are they?&rdquo; He said: &ldquo;The main body.&rdquo;',
