      'It was narrated from Abu Malik Ashari that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;People among my nation will drink wine, calling it by another name, and musical instruments will be played for them and singing girls (will sing for them). Allah will cause the earth to swallow them up, and will turn them into monkeys and pigs.&rdquo;',
