    hadithEnglish:
      'It was narrated from Abu Hurairah that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;We are more likely to express doubt than Ibrahim when he said: &ldquo;My Lord! Show me how You give life to the dead. He (Allah) said: Do you not believe? He (Ibrahim) said: Yes (I believe), but to be stronger in Faith.[2:260] And may Allah have mercy on Lut. He wished to have a powerful support. And if i were to stay in prison as long as Yusuf stayed, I would have accepted the offer.&rdquo;',
