    hadithEnglish:
      'It was narrated that Hudhaifah bin Asid said:\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) looked out at us from a room, when we were talking about the Hour. He said: The Hour will not begin until there are ten signs: Dajjal, (False Christ), the smoke, and the rising of the sun from the west.',
