      'It was narrated from Abu Hurairah that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;The Beast will emerge and will have with it the seal of Sulaiman bin Dawud and the staff of Musa bin Imran (as). It will make the faces of the believers shine with the staff, and will mark the noses of the disbelievers with the seal, until the inhabitants of a cluster of houses will gather together; then one will say O believer! And to another O disbeliever.&rdquo;',
