    hadithEnglish:
      'It was narrated that Jabir bin Abdullah said:\n&ldquo;The Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) passed by a man who was praying on a rock, and he went towards Makkah and stayed a while, then he left and found the man still praying as he had been. He stood up and clasped his hands, then said: &ldquo;O people, you should observe moderation,&rdquo; three times, &ldquo;for Allah does not get tired (of giving reward) but you get tired.&rdquo;',
