      'It was narrated from Abdullah bin Masud that the Prophet (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;If the appointed time of death of anyone of you is in a certain land, some need will cause him to go there, then when he reaches the furthest point that it is decreed he will reach, Allah takes (his soul). And on the Day of Resurrection the earth will say: My Lord, this is what You entrusted to me.&rdquo;',
