    hadithEnglish:
      'It was narrated from Ibn Umar that the Prophet (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;When anyone of you dies, he is shown his place morning and evening. If he is one of the people of Paradise, then he will be shown his seat in Paradise, and if he is one of the people of Hell, then he will be shown his seat in Hell. And it is said: This is your place until you are raised on the Day of Resurrection.&rdquo;',
