      'It was narrated that Qasim said:\nAishah said: &ldquo;I said: O Messenger of Allah, how will the people be gathered on the Day of Resurrection? He said: Barefoot and naked. I said: And the women? He said: And the women. I said: O Messenger of Allah, will we not feel embarrassed? He said: O Aishah, the matter will be too serious for them to look at one another.&rdquo;',
