      'It was narrated from Abu Hurairah that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;Every Prophet had a prayer that was answered, and every Prophet offered this prayer in this world. But I am saving my prayer so that I can intercede for my nation, and it reaches every one of them who dies not associating anything with Allah.&rdquo;',
