    hadithEnglish:
      'It was narrated from Abu Hurairah that the Prophet (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;The Fire will consume all of the son of Adam except the mark of prostration. Allah has forbidden the Fire to consume the mark of prostration.&rdquo;',
